#### ğŸ² Best "Board Game Cafe" Hack: 2nd Place ğŸ¥ˆ

![Image](https://i.imgur.com/bVAUlbn.png)

**Team:** Pineapple (@Jef ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸, @mayonnaise ğŸ‡¨ğŸ‡¦, @Rhea_K ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸)
