#### ğŸ’Œ Best "Stoop Sale" Hack: 1st Place ğŸ¥‡

![The Great Christmas Rescue](https://i.imgur.com/EEjFsuz.png)

**Team:** Code Riders (@AnA ğŸ‡§ğŸ‡©, @K Om Senapati ğŸ‡®ğŸ‡³, @CodeIt ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸)
